      <title>DraftKings 提高了客户增长的销售预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-03/draftkings-boosts-sales-forecast-on-customer-growth-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在线博彩巨头 DraftKings Inc. 上调了年度销售和利润目标，因为这家在线博彩巨头看到客户和博彩收入持续增长。首席执行官杰森罗宾斯讨论了新举措以及他们如何尝试优化营销组合。他在“彭博市场”上发表讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-03/draftkings-boosts-sales-forecast-on-customer-growth-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 17:17:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Coinbase 的 Haas 在股价下跌后表示“这只是加密货币领域的又一天”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/coinbase-s-haas-says-just-another-day-in-crypto-after-stock-decline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Coinbase Global Inc. 首席财务官阿莱西亚·哈斯 (Alesia Haas) 为该加密货币交易所不断上升的费用和数字资产行业的波动性辩护，尽管该公司第一季度业绩好于预期，但该公司股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/coinbase-s-haas-says-just-another-day-in-crypto-after-stock-decline</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 17:03:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
